cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG

This paper deals with image manipulation and style transfer, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The focus on mobile platforms and GPU acceleration suggests a potential fit for the multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) categories. Finally, the use of neural networks and optimization techniques may also make this paper relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) category.
